data.description: Location, Location, Location!!! This property feels extra private as it is situated at the end of a cul de sac with no neighbors to one side. Step inside this home and fall in love with its very open living/kitchen/dining space. Home has 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Complete with an updated kitchen, new carpet throughout, newer water heater, AC blower, fireplace insert, and your very own apricot fruit tree! Bonus: Matching refrigerator to stay! Excellent school district and close proximity to tons of shopping and dining.
